# Spec-driven design development

This project uses a **pragmatic spec-driven design development** approach. The spec is the single source of truth for what will be built. The workflow is **perpetual**: new knowledge automatically triggers extraction, validation, and refinement.

---

## Workflow overview

```mermaid
