## The 8 UX artefacts (spec pack)

All live under `spec/`:

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `scope.md` | Product/scope — what, for whom, success criteria, in/out of scope, domain, stakeholders |
| `roles-permissions.md` | Roles and permission matrix |
| `flows.md` | Core user flows with steps and decision points |
| `ia-screens.md` | Information architecture / screen list / sitemap |
| `design-spec.md` | Design spec — tokens, components, states (Fluent 2) |
| `key-screens.md` | Key screen specs — complex layouts, critical behaviour |
| `data-entities.md` | Data/entity overview — entities, attributes, relationships |
| `validation-edge-cases.md` | Edge cases, validation, empty states, permission behaviour |

When editing or generating content that affects the product, update the relevant spec file(s).

